      "date": "2013-11-13 09:51:27.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Abandoned\n\nA Chris has taken such a disliking to my TEST and after consultation with my management, their management, the Queen, my MP, my mum, my boys, my boys teaches and the local community policeman I have decided that for the good of all I will for now abandon this patch. But I do earnestly retain the right to resubmit it at anytime in the future that I feel would benefit the world at large.",
