      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.4/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/b6fec1dc-4c57-11e3-826a-52540035b04c).  Ran 19 tests.  No failures.",
